p\">8<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-8\"> </a></td><td>Hematopoietic, lymphoid tissue: Myeloid (8)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">9<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-9\"> </a></td><td>Hematopoietic, lymphoid tissue: B-Cell (9)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">10<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-10\"> </a></td><td>Hematopoietic, lymphoid tissue: T-Cell, NK-Cell (10)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">11<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-11\"> </a></td><td>Hematopoietic, lymphoid tissue: Hodgkin Lymphoma (11)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">12<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-12\"> </a></td><td>Hematopoietic, lymphoid tissue: Mast-cell (12)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">13<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-13\"> </a></td><td>Hematopoietic, lymphoid tissue: Histiocytes, Accessory Lymphoid cells (13)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">14<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-14\"> </a></td><td>Hematopoietic, lymphoid tissue: Unspecified types (14)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">15<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-15\"> </a></td><td>Kaposi sarcoma (15)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">16<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-16\"> </a></td><td>Other specified (16)</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">17<a name=\"CRMorphologyGroupCS-17\"> </a></td><td>Unspecified (17)</td></tr></table></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
